title: Boogie Zeits 2/18: Rod Blagojevich, Rosario Dawson, Pier One, Kaitlin Bennett
itunes:title: Boogie Zeits 2/18: Rod Blagojevich, Rosario Dawson, Pier One, Kaitlin Bennett
description:
On this edition of Boogie Zeits Jack and Miles discuss Rod Blagojevich getting his sentence commuted, Rosario Dawson releases statement on perceived coming out via Instagram, Pier One has filed for bankruptcy, and Kaitlin Bennett, Kent State gun girl and alleged pants pooper, visited Ohio State and was not welcome.
